List
====

List is a plugin which permits to manage ajax table. The table structure is defined in controller. 
It generates an action +list[_name]+ in controller and an helper for views.

It's a fork of Kame which refers to the japanese turtle äº€. 

Example
=======

  TurtleController < ApplicationController
    list :turtles do |t|
      t.column :name
      t.column :weight
      t.column :name, :though=>:country
      t.action :update
      t.action :delete 
    end

    def index
    end

    # Manage action create, update...

  end


